<subSubSection pageId="47" pageNumber="100" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="47" pageNumber="100">Geographical distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="47" pageNumber="100">
Northern Namibia and across the Kunene in southern Angola (
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 16" captionStartId="F16" captionText="Figure 16. Distributions of collection records of Bembix spp.: a Bembix triangulifera b Bembix ulula c Bembix venusta d Bembix zinni." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11865" pageId="47" pageNumber="100">Fig. 16c</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
